OL,5, The leader of the British Virgin       
OL,6, Islands (BVI) has been arrested for    
OL,7, alleged drug smuggling and money       
OL,8, laundering in the US.                  
OL,10,FPremier Andrew Fahie was detained in   
OL,11,FMiami by US agents posing as cocaine   
OL,12,Ftraffickers from a Mexican drug cartel.
OL,14,FHe agreed a $700,000 (#560,000) payment
OL,15,Fto allow traffickers to use BVI ports  
OL,16,Fwith an undercover informant, charges  
OL,17,Ffiled in the US said.                  
OL,19,FForeign Secretary Liz Truss has said   
OL,20,Fshe was "appalled" by the allegations. 
